title: I want to know how to find the functions implementated in torch. _C.
body_html:
Hi,

I am very sorry for bothering you for this problem. I often find torch._C in python source code. But I can't find it in this repository. Like torch._C._nn.nll_loss(). Could you please tell me how to find it? What is the rule finding the corresponding c source code?

Thank you very much!

Liu
